pull.title: Use background priority for all but the GUI thread on Windows
pull.body:
As an alternative to https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/161 we can run the whole process in background mode (excluding the GUI thread). This is recomended by Microsoft for I/O intensive services/daemons (http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms686219%28v=vs.85%29.aspx) especially if run at system startup.

Discussion: http://www.bitcoin.org/smf/index.php?topic=5982.0
